			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Today I’m going to be talking about SnowForecast, available on the App Store. This is the iOS version of the immensely popular <a href="http://www.snow-forecast.com/">Snow Forecast</a> website that, really, needs no introduction.</p>
<p>So, what features does the mobile app offer over the website? First-off, there’s the ability to find resorts nearby. Sitting in London, UK, my nearest resort is Pen-y-Fan in Wales (wonderful&#8230;), but this feature becomes many more times useful when you’re up in the mountains. For instance, I’m heading to Val Thorens in January; I’ll be boarding from ValT to Courchevel and Meribel, and it’ll be good to check on the weather quickly without having to search for the resorts individually.</p>

<a href='http://howardlloyd.co.uk/2011/09/friday-app-focus-2-snow-forecast/mzl-grnznleq/' title='mzl.grnznleq'><img width="150" height="150" src="http://howardlloyd.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/mzl.grnznleq-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="mzl.grnznleq" title="mzl.grnznleq" /></a>
<a href='http://howardlloyd.co.uk/2011/09/friday-app-focus-2-snow-forecast/mzl-qpqhoots/' title='mzl.qpqhoots'><img width="150" height="150" src="http://howardlloyd.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/mzl.qpqhoots-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="mzl.qpqhoots" title="mzl.qpqhoots" /></a>
<a href='http://howardlloyd.co.uk/2011/09/friday-app-focus-2-snow-forecast/mzl-tkpjozaf/' title='mzl.tkpjozaf'><img width="150" height="150" src="http://howardlloyd.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/mzl.tkpjozaf-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="mzl.tkpjozaf" title="mzl.tkpjozaf" /></a>

<p>In addition, you’re able to tag resorts as a Favourite, and they appear in the easily-accessible Favourites list. Again, this provides quick access to the resorts you care for, and really speeds up moving between individual resorts.</p>
<p>On the resort details page, you’re able to view Webcams, the regional Google Map, view a 6-day Forecast, and received snow updates for a single resort &#8211; handy!</p>
<p>SnowForecast is available on the <a href="http://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/snow-forecast/id418032026?mt=8">AppStore</a>.</p>

