			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This trip came as a surprise; both in terms of the opportunity and how quickly it materialised. I received a message from Dan on Monday afternoon wondering if I&#8217;d be interested in a quick trip to Laax. Once I learned of the details, and the price, I couldn&#8217;t say no.</p>
<p>We&#8217;re flying out on a Thursday night just before Xmas, boarding for 3 days, and then flying home late Sunday evening. There&#8217;s minimal impact on work, and the price (roughly £300 for flights, accommodation and ski pass) is fantastic.</p>
<p>Season 11/12 is shaping up to be the best yet, with trips to Laax and Zermatt in Switzerland, Val Thorens in France and Mayrhofen in Austria. Bring it on!</p>

