			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>After a few weeks of research, and a manic few days of full-on site-scouring, my third trip of the season is confirmed. I&#8217;m going to be heading off to Mayrhofen, Austria for a week in January/February. It&#8217;s a resort I&#8217;ve always wanted to board, and now I&#8217;m finally going to get the chance. I&#8217;m heading there with the Alex, Andy, Ali and Olly (who accompanied me to Alpe d&#8217;Huez this year) and Dan, who I&#8217;ve been to pretty much everywhere with.</p>

